---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me - Khasanbayev" description="Learn more about Khasanbayev, a passionate developer and technology enthusiast">
  <Navigation />
  
  <main>
    <section class="about-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-content">
          <div class="about-text fade-in">
            <h1>About <span class="gradient-text">Me</span></h1>
            <p class="lead">
              Hi! I'm Khasanbayev — a passionate backend developer with a deep love for transforming ideas into real, functional, and scalable systems that make a difference. I enjoy designing the invisible engines that power applications, ensuring they run smoothly, securely, and efficiently behind the scenes.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-image fade-in-delay-1">
            <img src="photo_2025-07-06_22-19-49.jpg" alt="Developer workspace" loading="lazy">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="story">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="story-content fade-in">
          <h2>About Me</h2>
          <div class="story-text">
            <p>
            Hi! I'm Khasanbayev — a passionate backend developer who loves turning ideas into real, working systems.
            </p>

            <p>
            Ever since I discovered programming, I’ve been fascinated by how code can power everything behind the scenes — from simple tools to complex web applications. I enjoy designing and building reliable, secure, and scalable backends that make the user experience smooth and seamless, even if the users never see the code itself.
            </p>

            <p>
            My main focus is on clean architecture and writing maintainable, readable code. I love working with modern technologies, frameworks, and tools — and I'm always exploring new ways to solve problems more efficiently. Using ORMs, databases, and RESTful APIs is where I feel most at home.
            </p>

            <p>
            Beyond code, I’m deeply curious about how things work and why they work that way. This curiosity pushes me to keep learning, experimenting with new stacks, and building side projects to test my skills in the real world.
            </p>

            <p>
            I believe good backend development isn’t just about making code run; it’s about making it run well — to create systems that are fast, secure, and built to last.
            </p>

            <p>
            When I’m not coding, I enjoy exploring new tech trends, reading about AI and software architecture, and sometimes working on small command-line tools or web apps just for fun.
            </p>

            <p>
            Thanks for stopping by my page — I hope you enjoy exploring my projects as much as I enjoyed building them!
            </p>
            
          </div>       
          <h2>My Story</h2>
          <div class="story-text">
            <p>
              My journey into technology started with a simple fascination for how things work and quickly turned into a lifelong passion for backend development and problem-solving. For me, writing code isn't just about making things function — it's about designing systems that are efficient, secure, and built to last.
            </p>
            <p>
              Throughout my path as a backend developer, I’ve worked on a variety of projects — from terminal-based tools and APIs to dynamic web applications that serve real users. Each project has been an opportunity to learn new frameworks, explore different architectures, and deepen my understanding of how great software is built.
            </p>
            <p>
              Beyond the code, I'm driven by curiosity and the belief that technology can genuinely improve people’s lives. I love diving into topics like databases, system design, and AI — always searching for better ways to create robust and maintainable solutions.
            </p>
            <p>
              When I’m not immersed in coding, you’ll often find me sketching new ideas for side projects, reading about the latest tech trends, or simply enjoying the creative process that comes with turning thoughts into reality. To me, backend development is more than a skill — it’s an art of making things work beautifully behind the scenes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="skills">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title fade-in">Skills & Expertise</h2>
        <div class="skills-grid">
          <div class="skill-category fade-in-delay-1">
            <h3>Frontend Development</h3>
            <div class="skill-tags">
              <span>React</span>
              <span>Vue.js</span>
              <span>TypeScript</span>
              <span>Astro</span>
              <span>CSS/SCSS</span>
              <span>Tailwind CSS</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="skill-category fade-in-delay-2">
            <h3>Backend Development</h3>
            <div class="skill-tags">
              <span>Node.js</span>
              <span>Python</span>
              <span>Express</span>
              <span>FastAPI</span>
              <span>PostgreSQL</span>
              <span>MongoDB</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="skill-category fade-in-delay-3">
            <h3>AI & Machine Learning</h3>
            <div class="skill-tags">
              <span>TensorFlow</span>
              <span>PyTorch</span>
              <span>NLP</span>
              <span>Computer Vision</span>
              <span>LangChain</span>
              <span>OpenAI API</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="interests">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title fade-in">What Drives Me</h2>
        <div class="interests-grid">
          <div class="interest-card fade-in-delay-1">
            <div class="interest-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                <path d="M9.5 2A7.5 7.5 0 0 0 2 9.5C2 14 6.5 18.5 11 22C15.5 18.5 20 14 20 9.5A7.5 7.5 0 0 0 12.5 2C11.5 2 10.5 2.5 9.5 2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Technology for Good</h3>
            <p>I'm passionate about using technology to solve real-world problems and create positive impact in communities around the globe.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="interest-card fade-in-delay-2">
            <div class="interest-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                <path d="M12 2L2 7L12 12L22 7L12 2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                <path d="M2 17L12 22L22 17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                <path d="M2 12L12 17L22 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Continuous Learning</h3>
            <p>The tech world evolves rapidly, and I embrace lifelong learning to stay current with emerging technologies and best practices.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="interest-card fade-in-delay-3">
            <div class="interest-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                <path d="M17 21V19C17 17.9 16.1 17 15 17H9C7.9 17 7 17.9 7 19V21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                <path d="M12 3C14.76 3 17 5.24 17 8S14.76 13 12 13 7 10.76 7 8 9.24 3 12 3Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Mentorship</h3>
            <p>I believe in sharing knowledge and helping others grow in their tech journey, whether through code reviews, mentoring, or open source contributions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding: 120px 0 80px;
  }

  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-text h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 
    color: #94A3B8;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .about-image {
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-image img {
    height: 300px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 365px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.3);
  }

  .story {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.3);
  }

  .story-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    color: #E2E8F0;
  }

  .story-text {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .story-text p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #94A3B8;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .skills {
    padding: 80px 0;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    color: #E2E8F0;
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .skill-category {
    background: rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.3);
    border: 1px solid rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.3);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .skill-category:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
  }

  .skill-category h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: #E2E8F0;
  }

  .skill-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .skill-tags span {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    color: #60A5FA;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .interests {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.3);
  }

  .interests-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .interest-card {
    background: rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.3);
    border: 1px solid rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.3);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .interest-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
  }

  .interest-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3B82F6 0%, #8B5CF6 100%);
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    color: white;
  }

  .interest-card h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: #E2E8F0;
  }

  .interest-card p {
    color: #94A3B8;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero {
      padding: 100px 0 60px;
    }

    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-image {
      order: -1;
    }

    .story,
    .skills,
    .interests {
      padding: 60px 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
  }
</style>